;
    pap-5.res created by SHELXL-2014/7

TITL 2sy_pq_agclo4_pagp_mo_a.res in P2(1)/c
REM Old TITL 2sy_PQ_AgClO4_PAgP_Mo in P2(1)/c
REM SHELXT solution in P2(1)/c
REM R1 0.194, Rweak 0.002, Alpha 0.039, Orientation as input
REM Formula found by SHELXT: C18 Cl3 Ag
CELL 0.71073 10.122142 9.646969 13.267158 90 91.7815 90
ZERR 4 0.00022 0.000219 0.000279 0 0.0019 0
LATT 1
SYMM -X,0.5+Y,0.5-Z
SFAC C H Ag Cl N O
UNIT 16 48 4 12 8 48
EQIV $1 +X,1.5-Y,0.5+Z
EQIV $2 1-X,2-Y,1-Z
EQIV $3 1+X,+Y,+Z
EQIV $4 1-X,1-Y,1-Z
EQIV $5 1-X,0.5+Y,0.5-Z
EQIV $6 1+X,1.5-Y,0.5+Z
DELU

L.S. 99
PLAN  20
SIZE 0.1 0.12 0.15
TEMP -50(2)
HTAB N1 O10
HTAB N1 O5_$1
HTAB N1 O12_$2
HTAB N2 O2_$3
HTAB N2 O2_$4
HTAB N2 O3_$5
HTAB N2 O7_$6
HTAB C2 O4_$3
BOND $H
list 4
fmap 2
acta
